text: Zigfrīds is a Latvian masculine given name derived from the Germanic given name Siegfried. People bearing the name Zigfrīds include: *Zigfrīds Anna Meierovics (1887–1925), politician and diplomat *Zigfrīds Račiņš (1936–1998), singer *Zigfrīds Solmanis (1913–1984), chess master ==References== Category:Latvian masculine given names
title: Zigfrīds
